senses.sense_definition: Not translated; still in the original language.

examples.text: The professor preferred to read the <w>untranslated</w> version of the novel.

senses.sense_definition: Not converted from a processed mRNA sequence into a protein.

examples.text: Mutations in the <w>untranslated</w> region can affect gene expression levels.
